<br>
+ Stealth items shouldn't effect detect hidden...  I said this earlier in the thread but will resay it now...  As I can see how a Gilly (camouflage) suit would make it easier for you to not be seen I can't see how it would make it easier to find someone else...  (I know these are supposed to be magical bonuses but unless they are gonna add detect hidden II, III, IV etc, I think that if you spend the points to spec 50 you should have an advantage over someone that didn't pay that price...)<br>
