I don't think they will ever offer a respec.  I have already been forced to re-roll once before because of flat out WRONG information that Mythic gave me about their own game.  The melee rogue was put into the game something like 2 weeks before the game was released.  I have been beta testing for them for months, to now change the way I have to spec to get the best stealth would be very, very wrong.  This is an unfinished class, and I would quit immideately if they made this change without offering a respec at the same exact time.<br>
<br>
It has been a torture to get to where I am now.  The melee rogue is very, very weak against monsters.  Gaining these levels was extremely hard, and it would be brutal for Mythic to now punish those of us that have suffered so long by changing the rules of stealth.<br>
<br>
Until Mythic puts re-spec in (if they do this at all) then these changes would be really, really bad.<br>
<br>
